# 3. BUILD + INSTALL MONADO (correct way)

```bash
git clone https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/monado/monado.git
cd monado

cmake -S . -B build -G Ninja \
  -DXRT_FEATURE_SERVICE=ON \
  -DXRT_FEATURE_OPENXR=ON \
  -DXRT_BUILD_DRIVER_RIFT_S=ON \
  -DXRT_BUILD_DRIVER_RIFT=ON

ninja -C build
sudo ninja -C build install
sudo ldconfig
```

---

# 4. FIX OpenXR runtime (THIS WAS YOUR MAIN ERROR)

## Create runtime folder:

```bash
sudo mkdir -p /etc/openxr/1
```

## Find runtime file:

```bash
find ~/monado/build -name openxr_monado.json
```

## Install it:

```bash
sudo cp ~/monado/build/src/xrt/targets/openxr/openxr_monado.json \
/etc/openxr/1/active_runtime.json
```

---

