# 9. ONE-CLICK SETUP SCRIPT (IMPORTANT)

This is your “future reuse fix everything button”.

Save as:

```bash
nano monado_fix.sh
```

Paste:

```bash
#!/bin/bash

set -e

echo "== Installing runtime path =="
sudo mkdir -p /etc/openxr/1

echo "== Finding Monado runtime =="
RUNTIME=$(find ~/monado/build -name openxr_monado.json | head -n 1)

echo "Found: $RUNTIME"

sudo cp "$RUNTIME" /etc/openxr/1/active_runtime.json

echo "== Installing library =="
LIB=$(find ~/monado/build -name libopenxr_monado.so | head -n 1)

sudo cp "$LIB" /usr/local/lib64/ || true
sudo ldconfig

echo "== Done =="
echo "Now run: monado-service"
```

Make it executable:

```bash
chmod +x monado_fix.sh
```

Run anytime:

```bash
./monado_fix.sh
```

