# 12. If SteamVR STILL says “plug in headset”

That ONLY means one thing:

👉 SteamVR is not using OpenXR runtime

Fix:

```bash
openxr-explorer
```

If runtime shows:

* ❌ NONE → runtime still broken
* ✔ Monado → SteamVR issue only

